      <title>备忘录显示，Meta 计划裁掉 5% 表现最差的员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/meta-is-planning-to-cut-5-of-lowest-performers-memo-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据发送给员工的内部备忘录，Meta Platforms Inc. 计划在今年裁掉约 5% 的绩效最差员工，以填补他们的职位。]]></description>
