      <title>越南与俄罗斯签署核谅解备忘录和数字交易以加强关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/vietnam-russia-boost-ties-with-nuclear-mou-cooperation-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总理米哈伊尔·米舒斯京访问越南期间，越南与俄罗斯签署了不具约束力的核能协议以及海洋研究和数字技术合作协议，旨在深化两国关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/vietnam-russia-boost-ties-with-nuclear-mou-cooperation-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 10:05:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
