      <title>拜登通过人工智能命令和智能汽车技术禁令加强对华限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/us-finalizes-rule-banning-smart-cars-with-russian-chinese-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府正在推出措施，支持美国汽车制造和人工智能发展，同时希望加大对中国技术的限制，为唐纳德·特朗普实施潜在限制做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/us-finalizes-rule-banning-smart-cars-with-russian-chinese-tech</guid>
